<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>273</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Vaihawm khat Isu kawmah zanin a hung,
 Hukdamna lampi leh vak thu dawng dingin;
 Lalpa'n thudik leh chientak in a dawng hi,
 &quot;Na pienthak ding ahi.&quot;

[V2]
 &quot;Na pienthak ding ahi,
 Na pienthak ding ahi!
 Ken tihtak taka nang ka hun hilh ahi,
 Na pienthak ding ahi.&quot;

[V3]
 2. Nanghaw mihiem chate, A thu ngaihsak un,
 Lalpa Isun guntak maia A gen chuh;
 Zie thu hi nangun mawk maiin um sak kiu,
 &quot;Na pienthak ding ahi&quot;.

[V4]
 3. Nanghaw zie chawlhna lopi a lut nuomte,
 Tatsate tawh kipahna la sak nuomte;
 Kum khawsawt a hinna neih na nawp uchun,
 &quot;Na pienthak ding ahi&quot;.

[V5]
 4. Lunggil a na muh nuom, vana deihtak te'n,
 Kawtkhak hawihtak bulah a hun na ngak ui;
 Zie la go tak thugen hi ngaitha zingun,
 &quot;Na pienthak ding ahi&quot;.</lyrics>
<title>YE MUST BE BORN AGAIN</title>
</song>